text: Ilmalya () is a rural locality (a village) in Baishevsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 205 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 101 km from Isyangulovo, 4 km from Baishevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Ilmalya
